    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>####引用</p>
<blockquote>
<p>1 “&gt;”</p>
<ul>
<li>“&gt;”<br>两种形式* 必须用在每次开始一行的头部才有效，且前后各一个空格“&gt;”</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<p>####代码高亮<br>利用来<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"></div><div class="line">```swift</div><div class="line">print(&quot;Hello World!!&quot;)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>####字体样式<br>“<strong>强调</strong>”，“<em>斜体</em>“，“<em>强调</em>”，“<strong>强调</strong>”<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<p>####图片引用</p>
<p><img src="1" alt="">  1处写图片链接  </p>
<p>####网站引用<br><a href="www.s-tm.cn">STM</a></p>
]]></content>
    
